function are called within a pattern or actions.
real parameters
	arrays are passed by reference
	variables are passed by value

to declare a local variable in parameter list, separate local variables form real parameters by extra space in parameter list.

ex. 
	function f(p, q,		a, b) # a & b are local
	{
		...
	}

	{ ...; f(1,2) ; ...}
	Note - no space between f & ( for function call. This not applies to bulid in function.
	default value of local variable is null for str & 0 for number.

use return expr to return the value from a function. default is null


